Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.96,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.67,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,She's at the festival after party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.59,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako goes out a lot now, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:24.38,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets a boyfriend, she'll be out even more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:26.47,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:36.41,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right. When Sawako gets married, she'll...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.69,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,We're not talking about some far off event like marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.83,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're on their way yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.70,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:56.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Until they get to the party, it's just the two of them! All by themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:00.76,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,"Did you wait long?" {so cute!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:07.35,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,"I just got here."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:17.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably exactly what they said!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.11,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to make fun of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.20,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What if the two of them don't show up??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.12,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. I would {\i1}so{\i0} punch Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I meant to take a peek at him in secret but he totally looked at me!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you so upset? That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.99,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.19,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so nervous, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.41,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really nerve wracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.62,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,And embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:21.78,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He feels the same way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:29.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You feel the same way too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:33.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:37.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, he only touched her with his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.92,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,No way, he didn't hug her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, barely touched her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.52,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:49.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had seen that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:52.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, still wrong! You guys are too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:56.94,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.84,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:03.02,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Some people weren't lucky enough to see so we were reenacting it for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:06.85,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right! Yesterday, in the classroom—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Joe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.56,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Can I punch you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Was what we just saw real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:17.40,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really like Sadako, Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean by "same here"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:21.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,When you said it was like a dream, did you mean a good dream? A bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you two just come together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:25.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:29.91,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I start from? Oh gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.12,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,In a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:34.83,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,yes. {HE'S SO COOL}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:39.99,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:40.63,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.99,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How did Sadako manage to get with Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.59,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I fell for her. {omg ahhhhhhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:01.23,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.71,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:05.66,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know either?! Poor Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.16,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.12,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:18.16,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,This is really okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you make me so nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.84,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.35,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:34.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:37.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you managed to win over Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:42.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't just faking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to pray too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.96,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us get significant others too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.56,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:52.48,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Why did things turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.73,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, they both look pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.32,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do magic! {give blessings}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:06:00.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Second year, class D, congratulations on sixth place in the school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.03,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:08.94,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still can't believe it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.43,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.97,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.02,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. {background song - want?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.82,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:35.58,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}thinks I'm an annoyance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:48.43,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Women!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:52.47,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:53.12,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,What do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:56.47,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What? Aren't you Miura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:03.93,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here? And with girls from another class!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:06.32,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't our class having their party right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:10.82,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to go, but these girls invited me out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:17.09,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you lonely, drinking all the way out here by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.84,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.67,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.17,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.08,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.79,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's a "confessed and successful" Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.10,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:37.55,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,This is just wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.54,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.51,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.15,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.47,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Just come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:48.32,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.90,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.31,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Were they really such good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.31,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:53.72,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.89,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make Sadako cry anymore, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:06.20,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear why Sadako was crying outside that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.54,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Cause she thought you liked someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.20,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.87,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Cause she heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.73,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,From me. {hahahaha}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.28,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that was your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.60,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:30.78,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,And it's Sawako, not Sadako!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.83,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay for me to call her Sawako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.16,Default,Miura,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm just using Sadako as a cute nickname for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.36,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you manage to tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.12,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What we talked about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:56.04,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What we...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.64,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.01,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.07,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.03,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:06.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.90,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.07,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.38,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.66,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you aren't the only one who thinks that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:21.13,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually ask her "Kuronuma, go out with me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No, but she under—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.62,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:28.19,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Does she really look like someone who would just somehow understand things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.34,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:41.26,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... Asking "Do you understand?" isn't the right way to do it.{\i0} {what he asked at the karaoke place}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.62,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.27,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.98,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.82,Marriage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(674,305)\frz9.056}Marr
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:52.82,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...Married?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:52.82,Marriage,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz346.437\pos(631,526)}iage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.50,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.19,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.67,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.24,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think helped you two get this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.08,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Let...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:06.96,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Let?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:10.09,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.03,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.94,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{so cute omg!!}Please let me think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.68,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:27.47,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's okay to not go after her and explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.29,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.06,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is it that things are like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:37.07,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... Worst case scenario, she might say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.70,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't understand jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:45.37,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks you're serious, and when you tell her you're not,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.36,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,she'll be so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.94,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So upset...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:54.52,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's not a question of asking her out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:58.18,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,She might turn you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:03.74,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:11.53,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.78,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:17.73,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try not to stay out too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.05,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.75,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.84,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:36.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to get married, how would you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.64,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Forget I asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.18,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.88,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.82,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:21.03,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:25.61,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,About... Getting married, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:33.25,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya, are you saying that was a misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.57,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.21,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You can hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:44.17,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Even I didn't really take that seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:48.20,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it was Mr. Arai who said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:49.20,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.57,0:12:51.70,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:53.79,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:13:00.71,Sadako Bubbles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}{\pos(963,148)}Let me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.71,Sadako Bubbles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}{\pos(302,136)}Let me fantasize about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.80,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hide... I need to find a hole and hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:08.55,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.92,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to make you misunderstand things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:15.34,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.34,0:13:20.83,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,The idea was so beautiful that I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:27.81,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:38.00,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have asked if you understood. {referencing karaoke room again}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.21,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:49.98,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,This is too important not to say straight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.43,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never move forward otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.54,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:01.82,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always take care of you. {oh my goddddddd}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.52,0:14:07.11,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:09.20,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.10,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:30.23,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I also have something important to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.05,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.29,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hate me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.85,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say, I'll never hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:43.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't look at you without hidden desires anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:49.41,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could hate you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:55.11,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we had nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.45,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.14,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,We can see what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:03.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I just think they look really good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:09.01,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I feel bad for saying that he's the most distant from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.56,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you say that to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.60,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.76,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.30,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:22.31,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Just before they started being really awkward with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.31,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:30.63,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.65,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Everything turned out okay in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.21,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.99,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the girls from the other class!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.16,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.30,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Chigusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.93,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Class C extended their party too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:42.58,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.53,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sadako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.19,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Strawberry time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.13,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You guessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.53,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Sadako!
