Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.00,Yume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz6.017\c&H909F9A&\pos(515,377)}Read me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.67,Yume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\frz16.043\pos(309,193)\c&H61685C&\frx12\fry0}Note
