Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.67,Yume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\c&H8D9486&\frx18\fry10\frz19.528\pos(1099,324)}He was wearing \Nregular clothes \Nat the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:32.38,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems like it wasn't a dream!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:39.20,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sleeping made it seem like it was nothing but a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:46.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But all of these reminders I left for myself before bed...{\i0}
