Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:51.65,Yume,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs80\pos(653,235)}It's real
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:51.65,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:54.40,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.32,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Please go out with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.57,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.54,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It all really happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:17.75,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.22,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.48,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Something about my advice—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.00,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,With black magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako got Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:30.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's eyes supposedly turned red while he was confessing to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I like you. Like like like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally controlling him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.45,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.63,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,No pushing! Form a line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.76,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.72,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What are you lining up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:02.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly everyone who got advice at the Black Magic Café were able to confess and are now dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.52,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:06.21,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,To be feared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.55,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,and worshiped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.93,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,she's already a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.87,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Charge them for it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:13.13,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}F-Feels like I'm swindling them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:20.76,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, if she had that sort of skill the two of us would already have amazing boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:25.62,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Totally! There are only idiots, losers, and baldies here though!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:31.32,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad she doesn't have to worry about being bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.65,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.70,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me borrow a good luck charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like one of your spirit summons!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:46.39,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Kazehaya believes I have magic too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're still saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.15,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:57.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I said it wasn't like that! I've always liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.17,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:05.15,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's blushing so it's got to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.15,0:19:06.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:08.87,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,G-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:10.95,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,G-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.73,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:17.30,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya says he's always liked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.00,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he said it was like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:21.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you know about—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:26.06,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have such a large audience, even from other classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:31.23,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you make it crystal clear for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:34.35,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What is Sawako to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:36.11,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Poke, poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:46.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.08,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.64,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,So blunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He used such a real, direct word.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:01.80,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,My dreams really did come true, but it's really overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.62,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.31,Default,Takahashi,0000,0000,0000,,To sum it up, please look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.31,Marriage,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.31,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it exactly.
