Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:20.67,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone, please be sure to spread the good news!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say to leave me alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:26.78,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,They're so lovey-dovey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:30.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they were like that at the party too... Especially Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:37.09,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at them now, I can't believe I didn't see how perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:39.44,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,they were for each other until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:44.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is how it should be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.14,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:05.48,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one thought Kurumi would be the heartbroken one,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.57,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Sadako the winner.{\i0}
